events.name: Buffalo Bulls at San Diego State Aztecs

headlines.description: Adam Muema rushed for 230 yards and three touchdowns and Quinn Kaehler tossed a pair of touchdowns as San Diego State rolled to a 49-24 victory over Buffalo Saturday in the Famous Idaho Potato Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: SDSU pounds Buffalo in Potato Bowl

events.name: Tulane Green Wave at Louisiana Ragin' Cajuns

headlines.description: Corey Trim returned an interception 82 yards for a touchdown, Hunter Stover hit a go-ahead 27-yard field goal in the fourth quarter, and Louisiana-Lafayette held off Tulane 24-21 on Saturday night for its third straight R+L Carriers New Orleans Bowl victo
headlines.shortLinkText: ULL collects 3rd straight NO Bowl win
